497
00:26:47,599 --> 00:26:49,491
ublížíš tím Joon Hyun.

498
00:26:49,491 --> 00:26:51,293
Seniore.

499
00:26:51,820 --> 00:26:53,139
Proč mi to děláš?

500
00:26:54,596 --> 00:26:56,486
