541
00:28:53,553 --> 00:28:54,993
<i>Byul zmizela!</i>

542
00:28:56,438 --> 00:28:57,339
Co?

543
00:28:57,339 --> 00:28:58,651
Byul zmizela?

544
00:28:59,734 --> 00:29:02,871
Byul! Byul!

545
00:29:03,704 --> 00:29:04,911
