706
00:38:17,225 --> 00:38:18,756
Mimochodem, Choon Hee.

707
00:38:20,013 --> 00:38:24,358
Teď můžeme vidět Pána v televizi?

708
00:38:43,212 --> 00:38:47,142
<i>[Smlouva lásky]</i>

709
00:39:02,593 --> 00:39:03,927
